<font size="+2"><b>Documents concerning AAWS history</b></font><br>
Business Report of Works Publishing in full length<br>
Original Author unknown, perhaps A. Nonymous<br>
Edited and corrected by, and notes added by,
</center>
<p>

The unknown original author stated:
<blockquote>

Keep in mind, that one Dollar in 1938 could buy, what today 11.84 Dollars
can. A post card needed a 1 Cent stamp only and the average <u>monthly
income</u> of an employed worker was around <u>$40</u>.
</blockquote>

<p>
<br>

<center>
<img src="http://www.orange-papers.info/orange-june40-0.gif" height="977" width="710" border="3" border="3">
</center>
<p>
<a name="pg1"> </a>
<center>
<br><img src="http://www.orange-papers.info/orange-june40-1.gif" height="1153" width="713" border="3">
</center>
<br>
<br>
