<center>
<table width="93%%" border="0" cellpadding="5" cellspacing="5">
<tr><td>
<font size="4" base="4" face="Times,Roman">
<br>April 1939 until end of June 1940 covers a period of 15 months.
<br>2,405 books in 15 months makes for an average of 160 books per month.
<br>$2.50 revenue per book makes for $400 income per month.
</font></td></tr>
</table>
